channel.title: Close to up to date DeltaScape source Download
channel.description:
Before I start, I'll be saying this a lot of times... I do not take ANY credits for this source. 100% to Delta, and whoever helped him. Please don't ask me how I got this source. I didn't do anything mean to Delta. I got it from a friend. THIS SOURCE DOES NOT HAVE SACRED WAR (See in a picture) OR DUELING! THIS IS BEFORE IT!
Things you may wanna know.
There is 100% Barrows!
100% Clan Chat
Fixed X logging
Fixed Dark Bow glitches
Fixed dds/ags glitches
Account scanner, to check for possible duped items!
A scan thing? I never got it to work, you might be able to though.
Many others, but I don't know them all.
Enjoy the following pictures and videos!
Server GUI, handle everything from the system. No necessary commands! [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source1.jpg[/img]
Starting at lumbridge, and hans is your welcoming party! [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source2.jpg[/img]
Just some stuff you wanna know. [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source3-1.jpg[/img]
Correct teleports, barrows portal location. [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source4.jpg[/img]
Skillcape shop. [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source5.jpg[/img]
100% barrows (picture version of course, theres a video at bottom! [img]http://i623.photobucket.com/albums/tt311/chaospkers/source6.jpg[/img]
[url=http://tinypic.com/usermedia.php?uo=s6fQw%2FBQcrvqR5jY43KTIg%3D%3D]100% Clan Chat[/url]
[url=http://tinypic.com/usermedia.php?uo=s6fQw%2FBQcrt2OWEDQbHrJQ%3D%3D]100% Barrows[/url]
If you would like for me to add anything else picture wise or information wise, ask here. I'll be more than happy to take more pictures.
Credits
99.9% Delta and whoever helped him
.1% me for releasing :)
Enjoy guys, once again, I don't take any credits (except .1 lol) and will BE MORE THAN HAPPY TO TAKE PICTURES AND GIVE YOU ANYMORE INFORMATION YOU MIGHT WANT!
Download links:
MediaFire Download link - [url=http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?jnu5zdmnzzd]http://www.mediafire.com/download.php?jnu5zdmnzzd[/url]
MegaUpload Download Link - [url=http://www.megaupload.com/?d=0985C5IE]http://www.megaupload.com/?d=0985C5IE[/url]
If you would prefer and different file sharing website, tell me and I'll add it.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: February 28, 2009, 03:39:18 pm[/size][hr]Sorry guys, I'll fix that second picture and cover up that link :)
